  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-icon-button\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-icon-button/`\n**wc-mcp Health Score:** 95 (A)\n**Known issues:** formAssociated, _internals missing descriptions.\n\n### wc-mcp Tools — USE THESE\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `validate_usage`, `list_css_parts`, `list_events`, `get_design_tokens`\n- **Report wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens. Background, border, hover/active states. Sizes. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. MUST have aria-label (no visible text). Tooltip for sighted users. Disabled state.\n3. **Functionality** — Variants. Sizes. Disabled. Loading. Tooltip integration. Form association. Link mode (href).\n4. **TypeScript** — Strict. formAssociated. ElementInternals. No `any`.\n5. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. Equal width/height. CSS Parts. Focus-ring. Ripple.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** — Fix 2 missing descriptions.\n7. **Tests** — 80%+ coverage. ARIA label requirement. Variants. Keyboard. Form.\n8. **Storybook** — All variants/sizes. With tooltip. Disabled. Loading.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** — Twig-friendly. Action buttons.\n10. **Portability** — CDN-ready. Form-associated.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
